          "value": "<p>The vampire has these weaknesses:\nThe vampire can't enter a residence without an invitation from an occupant.\nThe vampire takes 20 dano de ácido if it ends its turn in running water.\nIf a weapon that deals dano perfurante is driven into the vampire's heart while the vampire fica com a condição Incapacitado in its resting place, the vampire fica com a condição Paralisado until the weapon is removed.\nThe vampire takes 20 dano radiante if it starts its turn in sunlight. While in sunlight, it has Desvantagem on attack rolls and ability checks.</p>",
          "chat": ""
